## Final Handoff

Once the QA report is complete and the sign-off checklist is satisfied, post:

> "✅ **Phase 4 — QA complete.**
>
> **[PASS / CONDITIONAL PASS]** — [Project Name] has passed QA.
> All automated test suites are green. [N] P0 and [N] P1 bugs were found and resolved.
>
> See `docs/qa-report.md` for the full report.
> Activating **Phase 5 — DevOps / Platform Engineer**. Read `.cursor/workflows/dev-team-devops.mdc`."

Then activate `.cursor/workflows/dev-team-devops.mdc`.

If the result is FAIL (unresolved P0 bugs or failing test suites), post:

> "🔴 **Phase 4 — QA: FAIL.**
> The following blocking issues must be resolved before sign-off: [list P0 bugs].
> Please fix and re-run the affected test gates."

Do not activate Phase 5 until QA status is PASS or CONDITIONAL PASS.
